        "gg5g09zhY8N_text": "<p>Absolutely the most comfortable underwear I’ve ever bought. They fit perfectly, stay in place, and feel like a second skin.</p>",
        "gg5qyYTYLNz_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gg6_EEbztta_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "gg8vkzyRom3_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-f2ab390a-662e-4a0e-bf4c-237bc7b9d578.svg",
        "gg9djR-c3ZU_childItem_0": "<p>reviews</p>",
        "ggAEVbUSJBl_text": "<p>Marc C.</p>",
        "ggAGzVndjra_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggD_fPnY0sn_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_0": "<p>Item Details</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_1": "<p>Shipping Info</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_2": "<p>Satisfaction Guarantee</p>",
        "ggFJhv6XtFa_text": "<p>Camelia J.</p>",
        "ggHxm-K0LAX_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggJai-mIzBo_text": "<p>Avery N.</p>",
        "ggLbdEuXnjp_text": "<p>Rated <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong>4.6</strong></span>/ 5 based on <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong><u>3800+ Customers.</u></strong></span></p>",
        "ggLi9e3uAk2_text": "<p>Olivier J.</p>",
        "ggMOFdfwuZp_text": "<p>Capture your furry friend's unique personality in a vibrant, custom photo tropical style <a href=\"https://geckocustom.com/collections/personalized-cat-lovers-gift\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>cat</strong></a> <a href=\"https://geckocustom.com/collections/personalized-beach-gift\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Hawaii Shirt</strong></a>! Perfect for the cat lover in your life, it also makes a memorable summer or beach trip gift! Make memories that last with this one-of-a-kind fashion statement!<br>&nbsp;</p><p>Every&nbsp;<a href=\"https://geckocustom.com/collections/personalized-photo-gifts\"><span style=\"color:rgb(22,95,83);\">personalized photo gift</span></a>&nbsp;is special and unique because we upload your photo, which allows you to express exactly how you want your gift to look</p><p><strong>Preview</strong>:<br>- Choose an option and upload your photo.<br>- Click [<strong>Preview Your Personalization</strong>] to see the preview.<br>- Double-check your options before purchasing.</p>",
        "ggMXtYiLE4i_text": "<p>UNREAL comfort</p>",
        "ggMh8UP1KeW_text": "<p>Satisfied beyond belief!!!!&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggNfcoKkxKB_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggRSQR38XsP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggSV8qjUIF1_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggVI69kLduJ_text": "<ul><li>Full-refund or replace a new item (No any extra fee within 30 days since your purchase) for faulty, defective or damaged products.</li><li>Full-refund if the item is not as described.</li><li>We have 24/7/365 ticket and email support. Please contact us at&nbsp;<i>support@hapyco.co</i>&nbsp;if you need any assistance.</li><li>For more detailed information and instructions, please visit our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://geckocustom.com/policies/refund-policy\">Refund &amp; Replacement Policy.</a></li></ul>",
        "ggWSJUxnYcX_text": "<p>The most comfortable…&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggY2hH_XtMS_text": "<ul><li>The above time frame is only applied for orders to the US with standard shipping methods.</li><li>International orders: It may take 2-5 days longer due to the customs clearance process.</li><li><strong>Orders can be cancelled or modified only within 2 hours after being placed.</strong></li><li>Learn more about Shipping Policy&nbsp;<a href=\"https://geckocustom.com/policies/shipping-policy\">here.</a></li><li>For more detailed information and instructions, please visit our<a href=\"https://geckocustom.com/policies/refund-policy\"><span style=\"color:rgb(22,95,83);\">&nbsp;</span>Refund &amp; Replacement Policy.</a></li></ul>",
        "ggZ5ZjGQGbG_text": "<p>These boxers are like a hug—soft, supportive, and luxurious. They stay in place all day, even after multiple washes.&nbsp;</p>",
        "gg_q4SQCEgL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggaAE89r1UW_text": "<p>I’ve tried many brands but..</p>",
        "ggcrnmF_lIE_text": "<p>I’ve tried many brands, but these boxers are on a whole different level. They’re incredibly soft, supportive, and durable.</p>",
        "ggdBeG9LSOZ_text": "<p>My partner says they’re the most comfortable he’s ever worn. After multiple washes, they keep their shape and softness.</p>",
        "ggeny5F_KBU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "gghO-CfoMnU_text": "<p>No odor or sweat, this bamboo really works!</p>",
        "ggiBPVdR7g-_text": "<p>As a runner, finding the right underwear is crucial. These offer excellent support and breathability. They keep me dry and comfortable</p>",
        "ggiCWw-UEx6_text": "<p>Jason K.</p>",
        "ggpTskvks_G_text": "<p>Two weeks of walking around Europe, constantly adjusting and sweating. After switching to Boxhero, the comfort blew me away. 100% satisfied!</p>",
        "ggs_s6lEDOC_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-625369882908688947"
    },
    "gp_section_625369882925466163": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "9a5460415ec433dbbc15cf9ebd4d20b4ce04fd53edd4d5753a43a5dea93f4d5f_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggQ0Wtpv_Ah_label": "<p>TRY IT RISK-FREE – TODAY AT 50% OFF!</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_0": "<p>What is bamboo fibre and why is it used for boxer shorts?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_1": "<p>Why do dermatologists recommend bamboo fibre boxers? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_2": "<p>How does the breathability of bamboo fibre boxers differ from other materials? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_3": "<p>What does the “buy 2 + 3 free” offer mean? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_4": "<p>How does the durability of bamboo fibre boxers compare to traditional boxers? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_5": "<p>Are bamboo fibre boxers suitable for sensitive skin? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_6": "<p>Can I wash bamboo fibre boxers in the washing machine? </p>",
        "ggRO0x1JBf5_text": "<p>Bamboo fibre is a natural material that’s increasingly appreciated for its soft, breathable, and environmentally friendly properties. It’s used in the manufacture of our boxer shorts to provide optimal comfort and promote better intimate hygiene.</p>",
        "ggX2EniVm9q_text": "FAQ",
        "ggXHYiMjwOM_text": "<p>Dermatologists recommend our bamboo fibre boxers because of their softness and their ability to reduce unpleasant friction, helping to maintain impeccable hygiene in intimate areas.</p>",
        "gggxLjRu8yN_text": "<p>The exceptional breathability of our bamboo fibre boxers allows air to circulate, reducing humidity and perspiration. You will always feel comfortable and fresh, whatever your activity.</p>",
        "ggkDSqjyiH9_text": "<p>Bamboo fibre boxer shorts are designed for added durability thanks to their high-quality material. They are more resistant to wear and last longer than regular boxers.</p>",
        "ggkYAJ7acNt_text": "<p>Yes, our bamboo fibre boxers are machine-washable. Please follow the care instructions included with your boxers for best washing practices.</p>",
        "ggmkvDRWsjL_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>45-day</strong></span> money -back guarantee</p>",
        "ggoQB6YO3wQ_text": "<p>Yes, in general, bamboo fibre boxers are suitable for sensitive skin due to their softness and ability to reduce skin irritation. However, if you have specific concerns, we recommend consulting a healthcare professional.</p>",
        "ggrxGymrlkU_text": "<p>Our special offer allows you to buy 2 bamboo fibre boxer shorts and receive 3 free. This is a limited opportunity to renew your collection of high-quality underwear. Not to be missed!</p>",
        "ggvyreBNINt_text": "<p>Still have questions ? Check here</p>",
        "ggxet32tdWW_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>free returns</strong></span><strong>,</strong> NO QUESTIONS ASKED </p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-625369882925466163"
    },
